# Data Directory

This directory contains the training dataset for all detection agents.

## Dataset

**Source:** [Kaggle - Synthetic Transaction Monitoring Dataset (AML)](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/berkanoztas/synthetic-transaction-monitoring-dataset-aml)

**File:** `Anti Money Laundering Transaction Data (SAML-D).csv`

**Size:** Version 2 (996.17 MB)

**Note:** The CSV file is not committed to version control due to size. Download it from Kaggle and place it here.

## How to Get the Data

1. Visit: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/berkanoztas/synthetic-transaction-monitoring-dataset-aml
2. Download `Anti Money Laundering Transaction Data (SAML-D).csv`
3. Place it in this directory: `data/Anti Money Laundering Transaction Data (SAML-D).csv`

## Used By

- Transaction Pattern Agent
- Customer Risk Agent  
- Network Analysis Agent
- MADDPG Training Pipeline
